        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-12-09 23:34:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nMike - On quick comparison with  dcaegen2/platform/cli repo, noticed vagrant is not included here.\n\nAlso the following is not under onboardingapi/dcae_cli - how will the pytest get executed\nOnly in dcae-cli: pom.xml\nOnly in dcae-cli: setup.cfg\nOnly in dcae-cli: setup.py\nOnly in dcae-cli: tox.ini\n\nAnd except blueprint-generator, all other code seems replicated here. Once this is merged (after jjb's are setup), can the duplicate code be removed from dcaegen2/platform/cli repo - any issue/concern moving forward with it?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "af2bfaec39e5d12974bda7e7e463fdf9718a2106",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 1071,
          "name": "Michael Hwang",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "mhwang@research.att.com",
          "username": "researchmike"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-12-10 18:53:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> (1 comment)\n> \n> Mike - On quick comparison with  dcaegen2/platform/cli repo, noticed vagrant is not included here.\n> \n> Also the following is not under onboardingapi/dcae_cli - how will the pytest get executed\n> Only in dcae-cli: pom.xml\n> Only in dcae-cli: setup.cfg\n> Only in dcae-cli: setup.py\n> Only in dcae-cli: tox.ini\n> \n> And except blueprint-generator, all other code seems replicated here. Once this is merged (after jjb's are setup), can the duplicate code be removed from dcaegen2/platform/cli repo - any issue/concern moving forward with it?\n\nI considered vagrant a deprecated legacy thing especially because the onboarding testing in DCAE MOD hasn't been determined yet and the vagrant uses docker host based runtime.\n\nThose files for pytest is under \"onboardingapi\".  \"onboardingapi/dcae_cli\" is the actual python module.  I moved \"dcae_cli/dcae_cli\" to \"onboardingapi/dcae_cli\" so we should be good for the testing stuff.\n\nWe can remove the dcaegen2/platform/cli repo.  It is an independent piece.  We would need to make sure people understand the use of dcae-cli is deprecated is all.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
